{"sn23.22:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 23.22 ","sn23.22:0.2":"2. Dutiyamaravagga ","sn23.22:0.3":"Nirodhadhammasutta ","sn23.22:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn23.22:1.2":"Ekamantam nisinno kho ayasma radho bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn23.22:1.3":"“‘nirodhadhammo, nirodhadhammo’ti, bhante, vuccati. ","sn23.22:1.4":"Katamo nu kho, bhante, nirodhadhammo”ti? ","sn23.22:1.5":"“Rupam kho, radha, nirodhadhammo, vedana nirodhadhammo, sanna nirodhadhammo, sankhara nirodhadhammo, vinnanam nirodhadhammo. ","sn23.22:1.6":"Evam passam …pe… ","sn23.22:1.7":"naparam itthattayati pajanati”ti. ","sn23.22:1.8":"Dvadasamam. ","sn23.22:1.9":"Dutiyamaravaggo. ","sn23.22:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn23.22:2.1":"Maro ca maradhammo ca, ","sn23.22:2.2":"Aniccena apare duve; ","sn23.22:2.3":"Dukkhena ca duve vutta, ","sn23.22:2.4":"Anattena tatheva ca; ","sn23.22:2.5":"Khayavayasamudayam, ","sn23.22:2.6":"Nirodhadhammena dvadasati. "}